premise_source_doc_sentence: In 2003 , Banks created and began presenting the long-running reality television series America 's Next Top Model , which she executive produced and presented for the first twenty-two seasons until the series ' cancellation in October 2015 .
The Tyra Banks Show , also known as and shortened to Tyra or The Tyra Show , is an American talk show hosted by Tyra Banks .

While Banks 's show covered a variety of topics , there was a sensationalized focus on current issues facing women , with often special episodes on America 's Next Top Model , which Banks herself had also created and which she still hosts .
Cycle 13 's Ashley Howard was also scouted at The Tyra Banks Show , while Cycle 15 contestants Jane Randall and Kendal Brown were scouted through a photo challenge on Tyra Banks ' website .
In 2007 Moore gained attention for teaching TV presenter Tyra Banks to breast feed on Banks ' television talk show .
